resources[0].properties.query:
//001-22 Azure AD: Conditional Access Policy Was Enabled
AuditLogs
| where Category == "Policy"
| where OperationName == "Update conditional access policy"
| extend State = tostring(parse_json(tostring(parse_json(tostring(TargetResources[0].modifiedProperties))[0].newValue)).state)
| where State == "enabled"
| where Result == "success"
| extend TimeGenerated == TimeGenerated
| extend OperationName == OperationName
| extend AdditionalDetails_ = tostring(AdditionalDetails)
| extend InitiatedUser_IPAddress = tostring(parse_json(tostring(InitiatedBy.user)).ipAddress)
| extend Initiated_UserID = tostring(parse_json(tostring(InitiatedBy.user)).id)
| extend InitiatedUser_FullDetails = tostring(parse_json(tostring(InitiatedBy)))
| extend InitiatedBy = tostring(parse_json(tostring(InitiatedBy.user)).userPrincipalName)
| extend PolicyName = tostring(TargetResources[0].displayName)
| extend PolicyID = tostring(TargetResources[0].id)
| extend TargetResources_ = tostring(parse_json(tostring(TargetResources)))
| extend ModifiedProperties = tostring(TargetResources[0].modifiedProperties)
| distinct
    TimeGenerated,
    SourceSystem,
    OperationName,
    State,
    Identity,
    InitiatedBy,
    Initiated_UserID,
    InitiatedUser_IPAddress,
    InitiatedUser_FullDetails,
    PolicyName,
    PolicyID,
    Result,
    AdditionalDetails_,
    TargetResources_,
    ResourceId
